{"tid":1573314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪有澳洲巴絲開咗Gladys Liu戰線?","createTime":"2019-09-16T03:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:07:39.000Z","uid":45684,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b96e8287c3bbe9ff342e96b492d296508d612f07","tid":1573314,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49679923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49679923&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2cc4723d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49679923&h=2e52c34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49679923</a><br />\ntwitter作戰時見到呢單新聞<br />\n<br />\n澳洲的中國恐懼症：華裔女議員涉北京統戰組織受到壓力<br />\n<br />\n香港出生的澳大利亞女議員因同中共的聯繫受到批評壓力，但澳大利亞總理斯科特&middot;莫里森周四（9月12日）為這位華人議員辯護。<br />\n<br />\n和莫里森同屬自由黨的廖嬋娥（Gladys Liu）是首位在澳大利亞聯邦眾議院獲得席位的華裔議員，她被指是同中國執政黨的相關組織的成員。澳洲學者說，圍繞廖嬋娥的爭議已經具有排外意味，可能會導致澳洲華人社區受到傷害。<br />\n<br />\n澳美同盟新動作 籌建新港迎美軍<br />\n恐華症？澳大利亞中國問題專家發生爭執<br />\n「我在澳大利亞，但感覺受到中國學生審查」<br />\n澳洲廣播電台報道說，廖嬋娥是同中共統戰部有關的幾個組織的成員。報道說，統戰部的職責是促進中共在海內外的聯絡工作，包括招募海外華人。澳洲廣播電台根據中國政府網站顯示的信息認為，廖嬋娥曾經是中國海外交流協會的成員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/mark-dreyfus-qc-mp-ms-gladys-liu-to-answer-the-australian-people-with-honesty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fmark-dreyfus-qc-mp-ms-gladys-liu-to-answer-the-australian-people-with-honesty&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=7bfd3b13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/mark-dreyfus-qc-mp-ms-gladys-liu-to-answer-the-australian-people-with-honesty</a><br />\n隨之有人開咗呢個簽名<br />\n而家美國有HKHRDA, 德國英國有動作, 澳洲有咁嘅彈藥無理由唔做嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ee85bc8f7f760181c5630512739fc93a93ab07","tid":1573314,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"澳洲撚留名"},{"pid":"8eb5830221ff7743631d98aec05c5e8923138099","tid":1573314,"uid":217184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96e8287c3bbe9ff342e96b492d296508d612f07","tid":1573314,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49679923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49679923&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2cc4723d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-49679923&h=2e52c34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-49679923</a><br />\ntwitter作戰時見到呢單新聞<br />\n<br />\n澳洲的中國恐懼症：華裔女議員涉北京統戰組織受到壓力<br />\n<br />\n香港出生的澳大利亞女議員因同中共的聯繫受到批評壓力，但澳大利亞總理斯科特&middot;莫里森周四（9月12日）為這位華人議員辯護。<br />\n<br />\n和莫里森同屬自由黨的廖嬋娥（Gladys Liu）是首位在澳大利亞聯邦眾議院獲得席位的華裔議員，她被指是同中國執政黨的相關組織的成員。澳洲學者說，圍繞廖嬋娥的爭議已經具有排外意味，可能會導致澳洲華人社區受到傷害。<br />\n<br />\n澳美同盟新動作 籌建新港迎美軍<br />\n恐華症？澳大利亞中國問題專家發生爭執<br />\n「我在澳大利亞，但感覺受到中國學生審查」<br />\n澳洲廣播電台報道說，廖嬋娥是同中共統戰部有關的幾個組織的成員。報道說，統戰部的職責是促進中共在海內外的聯絡工作，包括招募海外華人。澳洲廣播電台根據中國政府網站顯示的信息認為，廖嬋娥曾經是中國海外交流協會的成員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/mark-dreyfus-qc-mp-ms-gladys-liu-to-answer-the-australian-people-with-honesty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fmark-dreyfus-qc-mp-ms-gladys-liu-to-answer-the-australian-people-with-honesty&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=7bfd3b13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/mark-dreyfus-qc-mp-ms-gladys-liu-to-answer-the-australian-people-with-honesty</a><br />\n隨之有人開咗呢個簽名<br />\n而家美國有HKHRDA, 德國英國有動作, 澳洲有咁嘅彈藥無理由唔做嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:11:28.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"0f7b9280d0b3d1454143a507930b06dc169bf38c","tid":1573314,"uid":150842,"li